If you appreciate my work you can leave a commnent and seed this for as long you can to help me upload more.


Requirements: Android 2.1+
Overview: parallel downloading three files simultaneously

In pro version:
- parallel downloading three files simultaneously;
- accelerated download by using multithreading (8 parts);
- a widget on a home screen and a window over all windows with the list of running downloadings;
- downloading using only the Wi-Fi and start/stop at on/off the Wi-Fi;
- autoload of service of the program after the boot is completed;
- a sound and vibration upon termination of loading;
- planning of loading of files in due time;
- automation action for downloaded files.


Whats New:


- fixed bugs;
- added Settings-Menu (you can hide useless icons);
- in the Editor window has been removed &quot;http://&quot;
Earlier:
- menu and context menu on actionbar;
- catalogs are turned on/off a separate button;
- finished download is displayed in new window;
- setting speed and the number of sections through the slider;
- choice of the path to the working folder in the file manager;
- customize the interface through a color palette.


